<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789000' id='t-789000'>EJ: Finally, let's see what this looks like.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794000' id='t-794000'>There you can see mosquitoes as they fly around, being lit up.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797000' id='t-797000'>This is slowed way down</span>
